concept_ext = instance.get_by_uri(urlparse(
    'http://www.xes-standard.org/concept.xesext'))
cost_ext = instance.get_by_uri(urlparse(
    'http://www.xes-standard.org/cost.xesext'))
identity_ext = instance.get_by_uri(urlparse(
    'http://www.xes-standard.org/identity.xesext'))
lifecycle_ext = instance.get_by_uri(urlparse(
    'http://www.xes-standard.org/lifecycle.xesext'))
micro_ext = instance.get_by_uri(urlparse(
    'http://www.xes-standard.org/micro.xesext'))
org_ext = instance.get_by_uri(urlparse(
    'http://www.xes-standard.org/org.xesext'))
semantic_ext = instance.get_by_uri(urlparse(
    'http://www.xes-standard.org/semantic.xesext'))
time_ext = instance.get_by_uri(urlparse(
    'http://www.xes-standard.org/time.xesext'))
assert isinstance(concept_ext, XConceptExtension)
assert isinstance(cost_ext, XCostExtension)
assert isinstance(identity_ext, XIdentityExtension)
assert isinstance(lifecycle_ext, XLifecycleExtension)
assert isinstance(micro_ext, XMicroExtension)
assert isinstance(org_ext, XOrganizationalExtension)
assert isinstance(semantic_ext, XSemanticExtension)
assert isinstance(time_ext, XTimeExtension)
